How to use

It is recommended to write the following tokens: trmnt, dark, black background, hyper detailed, cyborg, hyperdetailed, robot, machine, cyberpunk.

What the model is suitable for

The model trained on images of robots, mechanisms and cyborgs in high quality. You can create large-format detailed images with just one button!

LoRA was trained on a variety of examples, so try combinations and share your creativity in the comments.

I trained LoRA on the Deliberate_v2 model, so it's better to work with her in pairs.

Generation at high resolutions is possible.

Which model works best with

It is best to use the Deliberate_v2 model, but you can combine this LoRA with other solutions focused on photorealism, model will work perfectly with them.

items.name: YabaL_Mix AniRealistic
items.description:
YabaL_Mix AniRealistic

(Renamed from AnimeRealisitc)

- This model is aims to merge images to create a realistic-looking result, as if drawn from real-life references.

  • All sample images were processed using DDtailer (default settings with a mask blur value of 10).

  • If Red_Pupils are not included in the negative prompt, occasional red color may appear around the pupils.

  • If you want an anime-style art, we recommend using R-ESRGAN 4x+ Anime6b.

  • If you prefer a more realistic feel, we recommend using 4x-UltraSharp.

About version

  • V1

    Original

  • V2

    It expresses the eyes with more detail compared to the previous version.

    and there are slight variations in the art style.

  • V3

    The background has been somewhat flattened in 2D.

    The eyes have become more natural.

    The hand proportions are still not entirely satisfactory.

    The drawing style has undergone slight changes.

Recommended settings

  • VAE : vae-ft-mse-840000-ema-pruned

  • DPM++ 2M SDE Karras | DPM++ 2M Karras

  • R-ESRGAN 4x+ Anime6b | 4x-UltraSharp

  • DDtailer. In the default settings, the value of Mask Blur is set to 10.

한국어

  • 실사를 그린듯한 이미지를 목표로 병합한 모델입니다.

  • 이전 버전 보다 눈을 좀 더 디테일 하게 표현 합니다.

  • 모든 샘플 이미지는 DDtailer를 사용했습니다 (기본값 + 마스크 블러 수치만 10)

  • 네거티브 프롬프트에, Red_Pupils를 넣지 않을 경우, 가끔 동공 주위에 빨간 색이 생길 수 있습니다.

  • 업스케일러에 따라 그림체의 변화가 있습니다.

  • 애니 느낌의 그림체를 원하시면 R-ESRGAN 4x+ Anime6b를 권장 합니다.

  • 리얼한 느낌을 원하시면  4x-UltraSharp를 권장 합니다.

items.name: Licking Armpit Poses
items.description:
Delicious armpit, you must eat it!
This pose has been carefully handcrafted (i.e. thrown together clumsily in gimp) to consistently produce a scene of one being licking the armpit region of another. Works with realistic and animated models, lesbian/gay/hetero/robosexual combos, different settings. Cause everybody loves eating/kissing/sniffing/licking armpits, right? And if you don't, well your loss :D

2.0: Added 2 more closeup poses. New category, full body, with 5 poses added. Reorganized and renamed files for better overview, also included a preview for every pose for easy reference. All poses feature normal, openpose and softedge maps, standardized their resolutions to 1536 x ca. 2200-2300. btw, gfpgan is recommended for face restoration, codeformers seems to have problems with sideway faces. oh, and for softedge maps setting controlnet to "balanced" seems to create the worst images, at least for me. sometimes playing around with controlnet weight settings can help alot.

1.2: Softedge variants added. They often work great, but sometimes they seem to completely break controlnet. Be prepared for everything :D As a special bonus for surpassing 100 likes with this upload i also created a hairy version of all softedge maps. They don't work out of the box, you still need to prompt for armpit hair, probably with some emphasis. Body hair in general is very inconsistent in sd, but those maps should help with that, especially when you want to generate people with huge armpit bushes. Don't expect them to work on first try, though. hf ;)

1.1: Mirrored variants for initial poses added. Also included normal maps, too, which are far more consistent, but less flexible than the openposes (setting controlnet to "My prompt is more important" might help with that).
1.0: Currently only features closeup pose of two standing/sitting partners in landscape and portrait format. More versions to follow. As you can see in my simple example prompts it shouldn't be hard to get the pose working. Best used with 3:2/2:3 resolutions.

1st part of my CIA - Controlnet Is Awesome collection. To be continued...

items.name: Teats (aka Crotchboobs)
items.description: Alright, the Udders LoRA was working weirdly good and someone requested LoRAs for other anatomical concepts, so here it is. Teats, (known as crotchboobs in certain communities). For some reason, this one was difficult to train, may be due to token collision with the base NAI model it was trained on – I posted both filtered and unfiltered versions, the latter supports humans/anthros better but could be tricky to make work with ferals. Sometimes gives weird wrinkles on realistic models, but generally works. Uses e621 tags, supports "breasts and teats" and "teat bra" tags somewhat.

modelVersions.name: Teats-NAI-v0.2
modelVersions.description: Trained both on ferals and anthros (and some AI generated humans) from e621 data, using e621 tags. However, due to token collision (apparently, NAI had human breasts labeled as teats in its data), it only works well on humans/anthro on non-furry models so I'd suggest trying out something furry-related like bb95, lawlass mix etc. I also suspect it's a little bit overfit because I tried out some new training parameters.

modelVersions.name: Teats-NAI-v0.0
modelVersions.description: Older version that was trained with higher LR on data without any manipulation done on captions (the concept was mainly labelled as breasts), shows better compatibility with anthro and humans. Compatible with the Hyperfusion LoRA somehow.

items.description:
I will achieve this LoRA in 10 days, please download it fast.

I've updated my training method for better compatibility, and tuneability. It is now less overcooked compared to old ones.

If you want her to smile, just add "smile" to the prompt.

If you want a smile with teeth, just add "smile, teeth" to the prompt.

If you want a smile but a closed mouth, "smile, (closed mouth:1.5)" to the prompt and "teeth, open mouth" to the negative prompt.

I've also tested its tunability with hairstyles.

See all of these comparisons in the gallery.

For how I train LORAs, see description of JAV Anzai_RI○N | Stable Diffusion LORA | Civitai

Must turn on Hires.fix

Hires steps:17, denoising:0.5+

Use DPM++ 2M Karras or DPM++ SDE Karras

Strength: 0.6-0.95

She might look like someone from real life, but she is not what you think. She is a totally fictional character.

items.name: Character |YeXiu& LordGrim& OneAutumnLeaf – Quan zhi gao shou (The King’s Avatar) 叶修&君莫笑&一叶之秋（全职高手）
items.description:
Recommended parameters:

推荐参数：

Clip skip: 2

weight:0.7~1.3

Sampler: DPM++ SDE Karras | DPM++ 2M Karras

Steps: 25

Size: 512x512|512x768|768x512

CFG Scale: 10

 

————

Instructions:

○ About Versions

-v1.0: LordGrim

Using v1.0 for LordGrim is more stable than v3.0. In v3.0, there is a strange logo on the chest that cannot be identified as Happy or Excellent Era.

To ensure stability, no outfit change is made.

 

-v2.0: OneAutumnLeaf

To make Que Xie appear, use prompts like "polearm," "holding weapon," "spear," but it may result in situations where it looks like the weapon is "broken" (as shown in Example 5).

To generate a 7th-level fighter's will, you need to select a good base model (preferably with female characters, rather than just male ones, such as Wintermoon) or add loras related to hairstyles. Use prompts like "long hair" and "blonde hair."

If you need the Sun Xiang version of OneAutumnLeaf, try to lower the weight on the face and change the hair color to blonde.

 

-V3.0: YeXiu MIX

It's a combination of YeXiu's different outfits and LordGrim. Since OneAutumnLeaf has a smaller proportion, it cannot be generated stably. To generate OneAutumnLeaf reliably, you need to download v2.0.

There are more hoodies by default. For other outfits, please refer to the table.

 

○ About Base Models

Common 2D base models can be used. For pastel-style ones, it is recommended to lower the weight on the face using lora block weight.

3D models (e.g., Guofeng, Never Ending Dream) and realistic models (e.g., Chilloutmix, RPG) can also be used, but it's better to use Asian facial lora for beautification.

 

○ About Background

If a white background appears, you can avoid it by adding prompts related to backgrounds, such as "outdoors," "sky," "cloud," etc.

 

○ About Outfits and Hairstyles

-Hairstyles:

The first season of the anime and reset manga hairstyles are "M-shaped." You can use "M-shaped bangs" and increase the prompt weight.

The second season of the anime, special episodes, and the movie all have a "side-parted" hairstyle, which can be achieved using "side-parted bangs."

Without specifying a hairstyle, the default ratio is approximately 3:7.

-Outfits:

Outfits are highly unstable, even if corresponding trigger words are used, you still need to add prompts describing the specific outfit (there's no guarantee it will generate). There is a lora for YeXiu's individual outfits, which is more stable than the mix, but it's not a perfect fix, so it hasn't been uploaded. It's available in the gallery. If you really need it (although v3.0 should be enough), you can support us on ko-fi.

The following table provides trigger words and prompts for outfits (examples use YeXiu's individual outfit loras for reference).

 https://docs.google.com/document/d/1rPFDLzRvjxeXuaMRH1duXU4gNGqrNSgxXS0FCGzqLPk/edit?usp=sharing

说明：

○ 关于版本

v1.0为君莫笑：

用1.0出君莫笑比3.0更稳定一点，3.0胸前会有无法辨识是兴欣还是嘉世的奇怪logo。

为了稳定没做换装。

v2.0为一叶之秋：

让却邪出现要用polearm, holding weapon, spear等描述战矛的prompt，但容易出现“断掉”的情况（如例图5）。

想出7阶斗者意志，需要挑选好底模（带女性角色的，而非只有男性的，比如wintermoon效果就好一些），或者增加发型相关lora，使用prompt推荐long hair, blonde hair。

不做孙翔版一叶之秋，想出的话，把脸部权重调低，然后变个发色（blonde hair）就行了。

V3.0为叶修MIX：

叶修不同衣服+君莫笑的混合，一叶之秋占比太小所以出不了，想稳定出一叶之秋需要下载2.0。

默认出连帽衫比较多。其他服装请见表格。

○ 关于底模

常用的二次元底模都可以，粉彩类的建议使用lora block weight把脸部权重降一点。

3d类底模（guofeng，never ending dream等）和现实类底模（chilloutmix，RPG）也可以用，不过最好加亚洲脸类的lora美化一下。

○ 关于背景

如果出现白背景，可以通过加关于背景的prompt来避免，比如outdoors, sky, cloud之类的。

○ 关于服装和发型

-发型：

动画第一季和重置漫画发型都是M字，可以用M-shaped bangs，需要增加prompt权重；

动画第二季、特别篇、电影都是46分，可以用side-parted bangs。

不写发型默认的出图比例大概3:7。

-服装：

服装极度不稳定，即使用了对应触发词，也需要增加对这套衣服的描述做prompt（也不一定能出）。

有做老叶单一服装的lora，会比mix要稳定一点，但也不是固定完美出图，所以就没上传，打包放在图库里了，如果真的确实非常需要的（不强求衣服3.0足够了），可以去爱发电支持我们一下。

以下表格是服装的触发词与提示词。（例子使用的是单个服装lora，仅供参考）

items.name: Eager Pet Pose / Pet Play
items.description:
Model for poses that involve the character squatting as if they're a pet begging for a treat. Should work reasonably well, even with SFW subject matters.

Adding spread legs to the prompt may also help if you're going at this from a less cutesy angle.

May leak into unspecific prompts somewhat (presumably the pet in the trigger phrase is somewhat to blame), so be aware that such prompts may result in weird results!

Otherwise I haven't noticed any particular issues with the character's anatomy when testing, but I'd assume the occasional creature may emerge (although the pose should be relatively straight forward so hopefully anatomy should stay consistent overall).

This was initially supposed to be called begging pose, but this version turned out to work the best among the ones I've trained so now we're stuck with this stupid activation phrase lol

The VELVIA model is a LoRA model trained using a high-resolution dataset and a new tagging method.

Updates include:

  • The photo training dataset has been reselected, no longer using regularized images.

  • The training dataset's resolution has been increased from 512x704 to 640x960.

  • A new tagging method and pyramid noise has been adopted.

  • 英语：Layered control processing has been carried out. Now it can be used in any model, any weight, any style, and it will not affect other clothes.

  • 中文：已进行分层控制处理，现在可以在任何模型、任何权重、任何风格中使用，并且不会影响其他衣服。

  • 日语：レイヤー制御処理が行われています。これでどのモデルでも、どの重さでも、どのスタイルでも使用することができ、他の服に影響を与えません。

  • 韩语：계층화된 제어 처리가 이루어졌습니다. 이제 어떤 모델이든, 어떤 무게든, 어떤 스타일이든 사용할 수 있으며, 다른 옷에는 영향을 미치지 않습니다.

VTuber Model

LoRA for creation of an original VTuber Model

(EN/日本語/中文)

|___________________________________________________________________________________________|

About this LoRA:

This LoRA is for those, who want to create their own VTuber model, but have no artistic skills in illustrating one by their own.

For this purpose, the LoRA has been trained on images with white background and a strait standing character to ease the editing process afterwards.

___________

>Trained with >CouterfeitV3.0<

___________

>How to use it:

Personal checkpoint recommendation:

nullV22_nullV22 + clearVAE

tmndmix + clearVAE

endlessmirai + clearVAE

notsoxjbmix1 + clearVAE

___________

Hard to use on:

AbyssOrangeMix

AnythingV3/V5

AnyLora

cetusMix

___________

IMPORTANT: I highly recommend using the OpenPose extension for ControlNet.

___________

-->Prompts: (simple background,white background:1.5), full body, standing, looking at viewer, solo,

-->Negative Prompts: cut out, cut head,(outpaint:1.5),extra leg, short legs, fat legs,

___________

-->LoRA strength: 1

-->Highres fix: Latent

-->Sampler: DPM++ 2M Karras

-->CFG scale: 7~11

________________________________________________________________________________________

Prompt example:

___________

Prompt:

masterpiece, best quality,1girl, full body,solo,(simple background,white background:1.5),standing strait, looking at viewer,open mouth, laugh,military uniform, pants, black uniform, gold patterns, hat, <lora:GoodHands-vanilla:1> vt <lora:VtuberV2-000007:1>,long legs,

___________

*Important keywords are marked >BOLD<.

*重要なキーワードは >太字< で表記しています。

*重要的关键词被标记为 >粗体字<。

___________

________________________________________________________________________________________

このLoRAについて

このLoRAは、VTuberのモデルを作りたいが、自分でイラストを描く画力がない人のためのものです。

このため、LoRAは、その後の編集作業を容易にするために、背景が白で、キャラクターがまっすぐ立っている画像でトレーニングしています。

This model was made completely by accident, I was experimenting with Two models

and Merged them to create this model, liked it so much that I would share it instead of it being for personal use.

Since this was merged with Lawlas, use the boring_e621 embedding though its fine without it. It's a personal suggestion from me

I'll probably make a version where the vae isn't baked in, though its a big maybe.

It's prone to generate hair that isn't the same color, I suggest adding the color of the fur with the hair, if it somewhat bothers you

It has a hard time generating tails in the right places in behind point of views

Hopefully you enjoy the model, if there are any problems, leave a comment

提示词中的“ulzzang-6500”或者“pureerosface”为文本反转模型，请自行下载。

"ulzzang-6500" or "pureerosface" in the prompt word is a text reversal model. Please download it yourself.

全身图容易崩脸，使用SwinIR_4x高清修复即可，如果你没有这个选项，可以在WEBUI-选项-Stable Diffusion里面勾选上“Upcast cross attention layer to float32”(在页面最底端)

The face in a full-body photo is prone to breakage.Use SwinIR_4x HD to fix it. If you don't have this option, check "Upcast cross attention layer to float32" in webu-Options-stable Diffusion.

items.name: Taelia, Snow Faerie - Neopets
items.description:
Trained on NAI / animefull

30 image dataset, mostly upscaled official art but a couple of fanarts too.

Trained for 10 repeats, 20 epochs (3000 steps) but picked 12th epoch as the best result.

Trigger word just taelia, but short hair and forehead jewel helps.

modelVersions.description: Trained on NAI

items.name: eGirls_v3
items.description:
Trained on a curated dataset of candied-out gamer girls, this LoRA is great for the eGirl Aesthetic. Colorful hair, winged eyeliner, all that stuff.

Here's an animation I made in Deforum using this LoRA (This the final edit, not how it came out of SD/Deforum). I have a post about making the video here.

I left out photos with makeup that was too over the top (band aids, obvious filters, facial drawings, etc.) as well as those with too many piercings, because they were showing up in every image.

You can buy me a coffee if you like this model.

modelVersions.name: eGirls_v3
modelVersions.description: Each version added to the dataset but for v3, stated from scratch again and removed all the images containing too many piercings, facial drawings, extreme makeup, such as band aids and super shiny noses, because they were showing up in every image. This version should be more robust and versatile.
